{
  "stem": "22174.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then, later that day, my father was ordered to come to the police.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my mother tried to persuade him to run away, but he wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And so he went to the police, and with all the other Jews, he was interned in Buchenwald, and never came back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was the beginning of his end, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And, by the way, that reminds me of-- my sister also told me something else, what my mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One time there's some Nazi officers came up to our third-floor apartment and wanted to get into our apartment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And so, as they were drunk, and my mother pushed them down stairs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they all fell down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My mother pushed them down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "She was a very courageous woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And she was very little, but very courageous woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the Kristallnacht?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After she pushed him down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There are other things I could.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody came and promised them-- when my father was in the concentration camp, somebody came and offered that he would get them out-- that he would get them out of concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked for money, and they gave him money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he came back and just was here and they couldn't get work yet, but he will, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he always asked for more and more money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] finally, they gave him all the silverware I think they had, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and he just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he also-- they were afraid they would blackmail him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Blackmail them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That they tried to get my father out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
